{"tid":1306611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中聯辦：香港市民和平遊行 展示了香港的文明","createTime":"2019-07-11T08:16:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T11:44:33.000Z","uid":144372,"like":2,"dislike":82,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"63e8f78711c70f37847ffe31f5b927accaa64622","tid":1306611,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:16:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=355040\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D355040&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8529ey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=e04f2ace\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D355040&h=739e80e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=355040</a><br />\n<br />\nNow新聞台】中聯辦主任王志民出席香港各界慶祝國慶七十周年籌委會時，首次回應近月的反修訂逃犯條例風波。<br />\n<br />\n他表示大部分巿民和平理性表達意見，展示香港的文明，但有少數極端分子衝擊立法會，令人震驚，應予以譴責。他強調法治和安定是香港的根本利益，中央支持林鄭月娥繼續依法施政、警隊維持社會秩序。<br />\n<br />\n他又認為香港少數人挾洋自重，亂中取利，香港巿民應予以反對。他指特區政府已承諾會更包容聆聽民意，巿民應給予時間和空間，相信未來幾年，一些針對香港深層次矛盾的政策逐步落實，巿民會獲得幸福感。"},{"pid":"3e371a5f3c7a6cda8b55f900ff6787681e41391a","tid":1306611,"uid":151256,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:18:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">一些針對香港深層次矛盾的政策逐步落實</span><br />\n<br />\nwe are ready <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要推咩惡法就一次過 最好而家推埋social credits"},{"pid":"39a231178c80d308c70edb3c3ed81b36dc6381bb","tid":1306611,"uid":21002,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"63e8f78711c70f37847ffe31f5b927accaa64622","tid":1306611,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:16:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=355040\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D355040&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt